platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Noodlecake Studios hits a hole in one with this great twist on one of our favourite golf games. Playing Super Stickman Golf 3’s wacky courses with Flappy Bird–style mechanics turns the challenge into a moment-by-moment struggle. Every flap counts, and when you time them just right—or reach the hole first in race mode—it’s exhilarating.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 飛天遁地，將哥爾夫球彈入洞
